description.en:
GLYPH Token is an ERC-20 token utilizing Ethereum based smart contracts to build a foundation that will serve the GLYPH ecosystem. This platform aims to change the landscape of international logistics through cutting edge blockchain technology.

Based on trust guaranteed by blockchain along with seamless interactions the GLYPH platform will save time and money while ensuring traceability, transparency and optimal security.
